      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUNK YARD LORAIN (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording three placings in a row before finishing fourth (17.59) at this track latest. Rates on top in this line up. JANA BLADE (7) collided with another runner last time and always well back when sixth (16.48) in a Grade 6 at Cannington. Has the ability and can atone with the right run. COOTAMUNDRA LAD (2) filled a minor placing last start at Cannington behind Formula Fire (16.18) in a Grade 6. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Expected to feature again. ZATARA MAC (8) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
